<item>
            <title>[HBASE-8589] add &quot;on-demand-only&quot; integration tests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8589</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Sometimes there&apos;s need to write an integration test that only makes sense for large amount of data, cluster, etc. It doesn&apos;t make sense to run such test on minicluster on single machine. We need to add an attribute or something like that to indicate that, and make sure mvn verify and IntegrationTestDriver do not run such tests by default, unless name is explicitly specified&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12648733">HBASE-8589</key>
            <summary>add &quot;on-demand-only&quot; integration tests</summary>
